#: tutorial.kolf:2
msgctxt "Name"
msgid "Tutorial Course"
msgstr "Teren za podučavanje"

#: tutorial.kolf:68
msgctxt "Comment"
msgid "<h3>Welcome</h3> to the tutorial course for Kolf!"
msgstr "<h3>Dobrodošli</h3> u Kolfov teren za podučavanje!"

#: tutorial.kolf:124
msgctxt "Comment"
msgid ""
"To hit the ball, press and hold the Down Arrow or left mouse button. How "
"long you hold down the mouse button or key determines strength of the shot."
msgstr ""
"Da biste udarili lopticu, pritisnite i držite strelicu dole ili levo dugme "
"miša. Jačinu udarca određuje dužina držanja tastera, odnosno dugmeta."

#: tutorial.kolf:180
msgctxt "Comment"
msgid ""
"To aim the putter, press the Left (rotate counterclockwise) and Right "
"(rotate clockwise) Arrow keys or use the mouse."
msgstr ""
"Da biste odredili pravac, obrćite se strelicama levo i desno ili mišem."

#: tutorial.kolf:289
msgctxt "Comment"
msgid ""
"<h3>Bridges</h3>Bridges can have walls on the top, bottom, left, or right."
msgstr ""
"<h3>Mostovi</h3>Mostovi mogu imati zidove na vrhu, dnu, levo ili desno."

#: tutorial.kolf:411
msgctxt "Comment"
msgid ""
"<h3>Everything</h3>Here's a hole that has it all. Have fun with Kolf!"
"<br><center>-- Jason Katz-Brown</center>"
msgstr ""
"<h3>Sve</h3>Evo rupe koja ima sve. Zabavljajte se Kolfom!<br><center>-- "
"Džejson Kac‑Braun</center>"

#: tutorial.kolf:524
msgctxt "Comment"
msgid ""
"<h3>Slopes</h3>Slopes are slanted areas of ground that push the ball in the "
"direction that they slope. This direction is shown when you choose <u>Hole-"
">Show Info</u>."
msgstr ""
"<h3>Padine</h3>Padine su nagnuti delovi tla koji guraju lopticu u smeru "
"nagiba. Smer možete prikazati izabravši <u>Rupa→Podaci</u>."

#: tutorial.kolf:579
msgctxt "Comment"
msgid "Hit the ball onto the slope and let it roll into cup."
msgstr "Udarite loptu na padinu da bi se otkotrljala u rupu."

#: tutorial.kolf:654
msgctxt "Comment"
msgid "Try out these different types of slopes."
msgstr "Isprobajte različite vrste padina."

#: tutorial.kolf:793
msgctxt "Comment"
msgid ""
"The steepness of a slope is shown when you choose <u>Hole->Show Info</u>. "
"Steepness goes from 8 (steepest) to 1 (shallowest)."
msgstr ""
"Nagib padine se prikazuje kada izaberete <u>Rupa→Podaci</u>. Nagib se kreće "
"od 8 (najveći) do 1 (najmanji)."

#: tutorial.kolf:876
msgctxt "Comment"
msgid "<h3>Walls</h3>Bounce the ball off of the red walls."
msgstr "<h3>Zidovi</h3>Odbijajte lopticu o crvene zidove."

#: tutorial.kolf:985
msgctxt "Comment"
msgid "<h3>Sand</h3>Sand is yellow, and slows your ball down."
msgstr "<h3>Pesak</h3>Pesak je žut i usporava lopticu."

#: tutorial.kolf:1040
msgctxt "Comment"
msgid ""
"<h3>Puddles (Water)</h3>Hitting into a puddle (blue) adds a penalty stroke "
"to your score, and your ball is placed outside the puddle."
msgstr ""
"<h3>Lokve (voda)</h3>Ako loptica ode u baru (plavo), na rezultat vam se "
"dodaje kazneni udarac, a loptica se postavlja van lokve."

#: tutorial.kolf:1111
msgctxt "Comment"
msgid ""
"<h3>Windmills</h3>Windmills (brown base with moving arm) have brown walls "
"(or half walls). The speed of the windmill arm may vary for each hole."
msgstr ""
"<h3>Vetrenjače</h3>Vetrenjače (smeđa osnova sa propelerom) imaju smeđe "
"zidove (ili poluzidove). Brzina propelera se razlikuje od rupe do rupe."

#: tutorial.kolf:1194
msgctxt "Comment"
msgid ""
"<h3>Black Holes</h3>Black Holes transport the ball to their exit, and eject "
"it at a speed in direct relation to the speed your ball was traveling. "
"Choose <u>Hole->Show Info</u> to see which Black Hole goes to which exit and "
"the direction the ball will come out."
msgstr ""
"<h3>Crne rupe</h3>Crne rupe prenose lopticu na svoje izlaze, izbacujući je "
"istom brzinom kojom se i kretala. Izaberite <u>Rupa→Podaci</u> da vidite "
"koja crna rupa vodi do kog izlaza i smer loptice na izlasku."

#: tutorial.kolf:1280
msgctxt "Comment"
msgid ""
"<h3>Floaters</h3>Floaters are moving platforms that carry a ball that lands "
"on it. Floaters' speeds vary."
msgstr ""
"<h3>Plutači</h3>Plutači su pokretne platforme koje prenose lopticu koja "
"padne na njih. Brzine im se mogu razlikovati."
